hadiths[106]{hadithnumber,text}:
7417,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : duniya momin ka qaid khaana aur kaafir ki jannat hai."
7418,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne Jafar se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina ki) kisi oopri taraf se dakhil hotey huey bazar se guzrey, log aap ke pahlu mein (aap ke sath chal rahe) they. aap haqeer se kanon waley marey huey memney ke paas se guzrey, aap ne usey kaan se pakad kar uthaya , phir farmaya : tum mein se kon isey aik dirham ke iwaz lena pasand karega? to unhon (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne kaha : hamein ye kisi bhi cheez ke iwaz lena pasand nahi, ham isey lekar kya karengey? aap ne farmaya : (phir) kya tum pasand kartey ho ke ye tumhen mil jaaey? unhon (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar ye zinda hota to tab bhi ismein aib tha, kyonke (eik to) ye haqeer se kanon wala hai (bhulaa nahi lagta). phir jab wo maraa hua hai to kis kaam ka? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! jitna tumharey nazdeek ye haqeer hai Allah ke nazdeek duniya is se bhi zyada haqeer hai."
7419,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna Anzi aur Ibrahim-bin-Muhammad-bin-Urwa-saami ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne Jafar (sadiq) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid (Muhammad Baqar) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki albatta Saqafi ki riwayat mein hai :  (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha :) agar ye zinda hota tab bhi haqeer se kanon wala hona iska aib tha."
7420,"Hammam (bin-Yahya-bin-Dinar) ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Qatada ne Mutarif se, unhon-ne apne walid (hazrat Abdullah-bin-Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke aap (sura) (أَلْهَاكُمُ التَّكَاثُرُ) tilawat farma rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-Aadam kehta hai mera maal , mera maal. farmaya Adam ke betey ! terey maal mein se terey liye sirf wahi hai jo tum ne kha kar fana kar diya, ya pahan kar puraanaa kar diya, ya sadqa karke aagey bhej diya."
7421,"Shoba, Saeed (bin-abi-Aruba) aur Hisham sab ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Mutarif se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha.(aagey) Hammam ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7422,"Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Alaa (bin-Abdur-Rehman) se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : banda kehta hai mera maal , mera maal isliye to iske maal se sirf teen cheezein hain. jo usney khaya aur fana kar diya, jo pehna aur boseeda kar diya, ya jo kisi ko de kar (aakhirat ke liye) zakheera kar liya. iske siwa jo kuchh bhi hai to wo (banda) janey wala aur us (maal) ko logon ke liye chhodney wala hai."
7423,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha mujhey Alaa-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah bayan kiya.
7424,"Abdullah-bin-abi-Bakr ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mayyat ke peechhey teen cheezein hoti hain unmein se do lot aati hain aur aik sath reh jati hai uske ghar waale, uska maal aur uska amal uske peechhey hotey hain, ghar waley aur maal lot aa-tey hain aur aamal sath reh jata hai."
7425,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Amr-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) jo bani Aamir ke haleef (dost) they, unhon-ne jange-badr mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath shirkat ki thi, unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat abu Ubaida-bin-jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Bahrain bheja taake wahan ka jiziya ley aaein, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne b-zaat khud ahale-Bahrain se suleh ki thi aur Alaa-bin-hizrami (Raziallahu anhu) ko un par ameer muqarrar kya tha. Hazrat abu-ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) Bahrain se maal ley aaey, Ansar ne Hazrat abu-ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ke aaney ki khabar suni to wo sab subah ki Namaz main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahunchey. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ada kar li, wapas huey to wo (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney huey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab unhein dekha to muskuraa diye, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mera khayal hai ke tum logon ne sun liya hai ke abu-ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) Bahrain se kuchh lekar aaey hain? unhon-ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap ne bajaa farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khush ho jao aur uski ummeed rakho jis se tumhen khushi hogi. Allah ki qism ! mujhey tum par faqr (gareebi) ka khof nahi (ke tumhen us se nuqsan pahunchega) lekin mujhey tum par is baat ka khof hai ke duniya isi tarah tum par kushaada kar di jaeygi jis tarah tum se pahley logon par kushaada kar di gaee thi. phir tum usmein aik doosrey ka muqaabla karogey jis tarah un logon ne aik doosrey ka muqaabla kiya aur ye tumhen bhi tabah kar degi jis tarah is ne unko tabah kar diya tha."
7426,"Saleh aur Shuaib donon ne Zohri se Yunus ki sanad ke sath uski hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, magar Saleh ki hadis mein hai : aur ye tumhen bhi is tarah lubhaaey gi (duniya mein magan aur aakhirat se ghaafil kar degi) jis tarah is ne unko lubhaya tha."
7427,"Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula Yazeed-bin-abu-Faraas Ribah ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab Rome (mojooda Itly) aur Faaris fateh ho jaeinge to tum kis tarah ki qaum hogey? Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ham wahi baat karengey jiska Allah ne hamein hukm diya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ya iske bar-aks tum (duniya ke mamley mein) aik doosrey se muqaabla karogey, phir aik doosrey se hasad karne lago gey , phir aik doosrey se munh mod logey phir aik doosrey se bughz mein mubtala ho jaogey. phir miskeen muhajireen ke yahan jaogey aur unmein se kuchh ko (hakim bana kar) dusron ki gardanon par musallat kar doge."
7428,"abu Zinad ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs uski taraf dekhey jisey maal aur jamaal mein fazeelat hasil hai to usko bhi dekhey jo us se kamtar hai, jis par (khud) usey fazeelat hasil hai."
7429,"Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, bilkul abu-Zinad ki hadis ki tarah."
7430,"Jareer, abu-Muawiya aur Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski taraf dekho jo (maal aur jamaal mein) tum se kamtar hai, uski taraf mat dekho jo tum se faaiq (achha) hai, ye laaiq tar hai iske ke tum Allah ki nemat ko haqeer na samjho gey. abu-Muawiya ne kaha : (wo nemat ( jo tum par ki gaee."
7431,"Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra ne hadis bayan ki, unhein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke Bani-Israeel ke logon mein teen aadmi they, aik kodhi safaid dagh waala, doosra ganja aur teesra andha . to Allah Taala ne unko aazmaana chaha to unke paas farishta bhejaa. to wo safaid dagh waley ke paas aaya aur us ne kaha ke tujhey kon si cheez bahut pyari hai? usne kaha ke achchha rang achi khaal aur mujh se ye bimari door ho jaey jiske sabab se log mujh se nafrat kartey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Farishtey ne is par hath phera . to uski bad-soorti door ho gaee aur usko achchha rang aur achi khaal di gaee. Farishtey ne kaha ke tujhey kon sa maal bahut pasand hai? usne kaha ke oont ya gaaey. (rawi hadis Ishaq bin-Abdullah ko shak hai ke usne oont maanga ya gaaey lekin safaid dagh waley ya ganjey ne unmein se aik ne oont kaha aur doosrey ne gaaey). to usko das mahiney ki gaabhan ontni di aur kaha ke Allah Taala terey waastey usmein barkat de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir farishta ganjey ke paas aaya to kaha ke tujhey kon si cheez bahut pasand hai? usne kaha ke achchhey baal aur ye bimari jati rahe, jiske sabab se log mujh se nafrat kartey hain. phir us ne is par hath phera to uski bimari door ho gaee aur usko achchhey baal miley. Farishtey ne kaha ke tujhey kon sa maal bahut pasand hai? usne kaha ke gaaey . to usko gaabhan gaaey de di gaee. Farishtey ne kaha ke Allah Taala terey maal mein barkat de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir farishta andhey ke paas aaya aur kaha ke tujhey kon si cheez bahut pasand hai? usne kaha ke Allah Taala aankh mein beenaai kar de to main iske sabab se logon ko dekhun . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Farishtey ne is par hath phera to Allah ne usko beenaai de di. Farishtey ne kaha ke tujhey kon-sa maal bahut pasand hai? usne kaha ke bhed bakri. to usko gaabhan bakri mili. phir un donon (ontni aur gaaey) aur us (bakri) ne bachchey diye. phir hotey-hotey safaid dagh waley ke jangal bhar oont ho gaey aur ganjey ke jangal bhar gaaey bail ho gaey aur andhey ke jangal bhar bakriyan ho gain . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke muddat ke baad wahi farishta safaid dagh waley ke paas uski pehli sura aur shakl mein aaya, aur kaha ke main mohtaaj aadmi hun, safar mein mere tamam asbaab kat gaey (yani tadbeerein jati rahin aur maal aur asbaab na raha ( , to aaj mere liye Allah ki madad ke siwa aur uske baad teri madad ke baghair manzil par pahunchna mumkin nahi hai, main tujh se iske naam par jisne tujhey suthra rang aur suthri khaal di aur maal aur oont diye, aik oont mangta hun jo mere safar mein kaam aaey. usne kaha ke mujh par logon ke bahut haq hain (yani qarzdaar hun ya gharbaar ke kharch se zyada maal nahi jo tujhey dun). phir farishte ne kaha ke albatta main tujhey pehchanta hun bhala kya to mohtaaj kodhi na tha? ke log tujh se nafrat kartey they, phir Allah ne apne Fazal se tujhey ye maal diya. us ne jawab diya ke maine to ye maal apne bap-dada se paya hai jo kai pusht se naql ho kar aaya hai. Farishtey ne kaha ke agar to jhoota ho to Allah tujhey waisaa hi kar daley jaisa to pahley tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir farishta ganjey ke paas uski pehli sura aur shakl mein aaya aur us se waisaa hi kaha jaisa safaid dagh waley se kaha tha aur us ne bhi wahi jawab diya jo safaid dagh waley ne diya tha. Farishtey ne kaha ke agar to jhoota ho to Allah tujhey waisa hi kar daley jaisa to tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir farishta andhey ke paas uski pehli shakl w sura mein gaya, aur kaha ke main mohtaaj aadmi hun aur musaafir hun, mere safar mein mere sab waseeley aur tadbeerein kat gain, to mujhey aaj manzil par Allah ki madad aur uske baad teri madad ke baghair pahunchna mushkil hai. isliye main tujh se us Allah ke naam par, jisne tujhey beenaai di, aik bakri mangta hun taake wo mere safar mein kaam aaey. usne kaha ke beshak main andha tha to Allah ne mujhey (beenaai wali) aankh di, tum un bakriyon mein se jitni chaho ley jao aur jitni chaho chhod jao. Allah ki qasam! aaj jo cheez to Allah ki raah mein lega, main tujhey mushkil mein na daalunga (yani tera hath na pakdunga). to Farishtey ne kaha ke apna maal apne paas rakho, tum teenon aadmi sirf aazmaey gaey they. to tujh se to Allah Taala razi hua aur terey donon sathiyon se naakhush hua."
7432,"Bukair bin Mismar ne kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Sad ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) apne oonton ke paas they ke unke betey umr (bin Sad) unke paas aaey jab Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekha to kaha : main us sawar ke shar se Allah ki panah chahta hun. wo utrey aur un (hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu)) se kaha : aap apne oonton aur bakriyon ke paas rihaaish pazeer ho gaey hain aur logon ko chhod diya hai ke wo saltanat ke barey mein aapas mein lad rahe hain (aap bhi apna hissey maangen) Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke seeney par zarb lagai aur kaha : khamosh raho ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna hai : Allah Taala apne us bandey se mohabbat rakhta hai jo muttaqi ho, ghani ho, gum naam (gosha-nasheen) ho."
7433,"Motamir Abdullah-bin-Numair aur ibne-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Ismail bin Qais ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Hazrat Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huey suna : Allah ki qism ! main Arbon mein se pahla shakhs hon jisne Allah ki raah mein teer chalaaya ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath is tarah jangein ladtey they ke hamarey paas khaney ko khaardaar darakht ke patton aur us keekar (ke patton (ke siwa kuchh nahi hota tha. yahan tak ke ham mein se koi bakri ki mengniyon ki tarah paakhaana karta tha phir ab banu-Asad ke log Deen ke mamley mein meri taadeeb karne lagey hain ! (agar ab main Deen se is qadr naa-balad ho gaya hun) tab to main bilkul naakaam ho gaya aur mere amal zaaye ho gaey aur ibne-Numair ne apni riwayat mein tab to nahi kaha."
7434,Wakee ne Ismail bin abi Khalid se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : yahan tak ke ham se aik bakrey ki) mengniyon ki) tarah ka paakhaana karta tha jis main aur kuchh (kisi aur khaney ka koi hissey jo usey paakhaana ki shakl se) mila hua nahi hota tha.
7435,"Sheban-bin-Farukh ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Humaid bin Hilal ne Khalid-bin Umer adwi se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : aik din (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se Basra ke aamil (Hazrat Utba-bin- ghazawan (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein khutba diya aur Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ki phir kaha : be-shak ye duniya khaatmey ke qareeb ho gaee hai aur is (ki mohlat ( mein se thoda sa hissey baqi reh gaya hai jis tarah bartan ke aakhiri qatrey hotey hain jinhein bartan wala undel raha hota hai aur tum is duniya se us ghar ki taraf muntaqil ho rahe ho jis par zawaal nahi aayega . jo tumharey paas hai is mein se behtareen mutaa ke sath aagey jao. kyonke hamein bataya gaya tha ke jahannam ke kinarey se aik patthar phainka jata hai to wo 70 saal girta rehta hai. uski teh tak nahi pahunchta aur Allah ki qasam! ye (jahannam) poori tarah bhar jaeygi. kya tumhen is par tajjub hai? aur hamein bataya gaya ke jannat ke kiwaadon mein se do kiwaadon ke darmyan chalis (40) saal ki masafat hai aur is par aik din aayega jab wo azdahaam ke sabab tang pad jaeyga aur maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (eman laney waale) saat (7) logon mein se saatwan main tha hamarey paas darakhton ke patton ke siwa khaney ki koi cheez nahi hoti thi yahan tak ke hamari baachhein zakhmi ho gain. maine aik chadar uthai to usey apne aur Sad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan 2 hisson mein taqseem kar liya aadhi maine kamar par baandhi aur aadhi Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ab ham mein se har koi shehron mein se kisi Shahar ka ameer bin gaya hai. main is baat se Allah ki panah mein aata hun ke main apne dil mein bada aur Allah ke nazdeek chhota ho jaun aur kabhi koi nabwooat nahi thi magar khatm ho gaee. yahan tak ke uska pichhla hissey badhshahat mein badal gaya. jald hi tumhen (uska) pata chal jaeyga aur hamarey baad ke ameeron ka (bhi tum log khud) tajriba kar logey."
7436,"Ishaq bin Umar-bin saleet ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin Mughira ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Humaid bin Hilal ne Khalid-bin Umer se jinhoney jahiliyat ka zamana dekha tha riwayat ki kaha : Hazrat Utba-bin-ghazawaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein khutba diya wo us waqt Basra ke ameer they. (aagey) Sheban ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
7437,"Qurra bin Khalid ne Humaid bin Hilal se aur unhon-ne Khalid-bin Umer se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Utba-bin- ghazawaan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, maine dekha main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (eman laney waale) saat (7) logon mein se saatwan shakhs tha khaardaar darakhton ke patton ke siwa hamarey paas khaney ko kuchh nahi tha yahan tak ke hamari baachhein zakhmi ho gain ."
7438,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : unhon-ne ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne arz ki, Allah ke rasool! qiyamat ke din ham apne rab ko dekhengey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya do-pahar ke waqt jab badal na hon tumhen suraj ko dekhney mein koi zahmat hoti hai? unhon (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : nahi aap ne farmaya : chaudahwin ki raat ko jab badal na hon to kya tumhen chaand ko dekhney mein koi zahmat hoti hai? unhon-ne ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne kaha : nahi aap ne farmaya : mujhey us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! tumhen apne rab ko dekhney mein us se zyada zahmat nahi hogi jitni zahmat tumhen un donon ko dekhney mein hoti hai. aap ne farmaya : wo ( rab ( bandey se mulaqat farmaeyga to kahega . aey falan ! kya maine tumhen izzat na di thi, tumhen sardaar na banaya tha tumhari shadi na karaai thi ghodey aur oont tumharey ikhtiyar mein na diye they aur tumhen aisa nahi bana chhoda tha ke tum sardaari kartey they aur logon ki aamadni mein se chothai hissey letey they? wo jawab mein kahega . kyon nahi ! ( bilkul aisa hi tha. ( to wo farmaeyga . kya tum samajhtey they ke tum mujh se milogey? wo kahega. nahi. to wo farmaeyga . aaj main isi tarah tumhen bhool jaaunga. jis tarah tum mujhey bhool gaey they phir doosrey se mulaqat karega . aey falan ! kya maine tumhen izzat aur sayaadat se nahi nawaza tha tumhari shadi nahi karaai thi tumharey liye oont aur ghodey musakhkhar nahi kiye they aur tumhen is tarah nahi bana chhoda tha ke tum riyaasat ke mazey letey they. aur logon ke maalon mein se chothai hissey wsool kartey they? wo kahega kyon nahi mere rab! to wo farmaeyga . tumhen is baat ka koi guman bhi tha ke tum mujh se mulaqat karogey ? wo kahega . nahi to. wo farmaeyga ab main bhi isi tarah tumhen bhool jaaunga jis tarah tum mujhey bhool gaey they. phir teesrey se milega. us se bhi wahi farmaeyga. wo kahega . aey mere rab! mein tujh par teri kitaabon aur terey rasulon par eman laya tha aur namazein padhi thin rozey rakhey they aur sadqa diya karta tha jitna uske bas mein hoga (apni neki ki) tareef karega, chunanche wo farmaeyga . tab tum yahin thehro . farmaya : phir us se kaha jaeyga ab ham tumharey khilaf apna gawah laaengey . wo dil mein sochega mere khilaf kon gawahi dega? phir uske munh par mohar laga di jaeygi aur uski raan, gosht aur haddiyon se kaha jaeyga bolo to uski raan uska gosht aur uski haddiyaan uske amal ke mutaalliq bataeingi. ye (is liye) kaha jaeyga ke wo (Allah) uski zaat se uska uzr door kar de. aur wo munafiq hoga aur wahi shakhs hoga jis par Allah Taala sakht naraz hoga."
7439,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( baithey huey) they ke aap hans padey phir aap ne puchha : kya tumhen ye malum hai ke main kis baat par hans raha hun? ham ne kaha Allah aur uska Rasulul (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zyada jaanney waley hain. aap ne farmaya : mujhey bandey ki apne rab ke sath ki gaee baat par hansi aati hai wo kahega. aey mere rab! kya toney mujhey zulm se panah nahi di? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kaha : wo farmaeyga. kyon nahi! farmaya : banda kahega main apne khilaf apni taraf ke gawah ke siwa aur kisi (ki gawahi) ko jaaiz qarar nahi deta. to wo farmaeyga aaj tum apne khilaf bataur gawah khud kafi ho aur kiraaman katebin bhi gawah hain chunanche uske munh par mohar laga di jaeygi aur uske (apne) aaza se kaha jaeyga bolo, farmaya : to wo uske aamaal ke barey mein bataengey, phir usey aur (uske aaza ke) bolney ko akela chhod diya jaeyga farmaya : to (unki gawahi sun kar) wo kahega door ho jao, main tumhari taraf se (doosron ke saath) lada karta tha."
7440,"abu-Zura ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( dua kartey huey) farmaya : aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ke rizq ko zindagi bar-qaraar rakhney jitna kar de."
7441,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba Amr Naqid Zuhair-bin-Harab aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Aamash ne Imaara bin Qaqa se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne abu-Zura se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki : aey Allah! aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka rizq zindagi bar-qaraar rakhney jitna kar de. aur Amr ki riwayat mein hai : aey Allah! (aale-Muhammad ko zindagi bar-qaraar rakhney jitna) rizq de."
7442,abu-Usama ne kaha : maine Aamash se suna unhon-ne Ammara-bin-Qaqa se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : baqadre-kifaayat (kar de)
7443,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ne jab se aap Madina aaey aap ki wafat tak kabhi teen raatein musalsal gehun ki roti sair ho kar nahi khaai."
7444,Aamash ne Ibrahim se unhon-ne Aswad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah ne kabhi mutwaatir teen din sair ho kar gehun ki roti nahi khaai yahan tak ke aap apni raah par rawaana ho gaey.
7445,"Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed ne hamein Aswad se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ne kabhi 2 din lagatar jo ki roti pet bhar kar nahi khaai yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gae."
7446,Aabis ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ne teen din se zyada kabhi sair ho kar gehun ki roti nahi khaai.
7447,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon ne kabhi teen din sair ho kar gehun ki roti nahi khaai, yahan tak ke aap apni raah par rawaana ho gaey."
7448,"Hilal bin Humaid ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi musalsal 2 din gehun ki roti sair ho kar nahi khaai magar 2 dinon mein se aik din khajoor hoti thi."
7449,"Yahya bin yaman ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham aale-Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik maah tak is haalat mein rahtey they ke aag nahi jalaatey they bas khajoor aur pani par guzar hoti thi."
7450,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, ham log usi haalat mein rahtey they. aur unhon-ne aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr nahi kya aur abu-Kuraib ne ibne-Numair se marwi (bayan) apni hadis mein mazeed kaha siwaey iske ke hamarey paas (kahiin se) thoda sa gosht aa jata."
7451,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wafat pa gaey aur mere taaqchey mein kisi jigar rakhney waley (zi Rooh) ke khaney ke liye thodey se jo ke siwa kuchh na tha main usmein se (paka kar) khaati rahi yahan tak ke bahut din guzar gaey (eik din) maine unko maap liya to wo khatm ho gaey.
7452,Yazeed bin Ruman ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke aap bataya karti thin : Allah ki qasam! mere bhaanjey! ham aik baar pehli ka chaand dekhtey phir (agley mahiney) pehli ka chaand dekhtey 2 mahinon mein teen baar bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hujron mein choolha na jalaa hota. (Urwa ne) kaha : maine puchha khala to aap ki guzraan ke liye kon si cheez hoti? unhon-ne kaha : 2 kali cheezein : khajoor aur pani. albatta Ansar mein se kuchh (gharaaney) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hamsaaey they aur unhein doodh dene wali oontniyan mili hui thin. wo unke doodh mein se kuchh Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya kartey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wo hamein pilaa detey they.
7453,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) duniya se rukhsat ho gaey aur aap kabhi aik din mein 2 baar roti aur Zaitoon ke tel se sair nahi huey."
7454,Dawud bin Abdur-Rehman attaar ne hamein khabar di kaha : mujhey Mansoor bin Abdur-Rehman hajabi ne apni walida Safiya se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki kaha : jab log 2 siyah cheezein : khajoor aur pani se sair honey lagey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rihlat farma gaey.
7455,"Abdur-Rehman (bin Mehdi) ne hamein Sufiyan (Sory) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mansoor bin Safiya se unhon-ne apni walida se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rihlat ho gaee aur ham 2 siyah chizon, pani aur khajoor se sair honey lagey."
7456,"(Ubaidullah bin Abdur-Rehman) Ashjai aur abu Ahmed donon ne Sufiyan se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, magar un donon ki Sufiyan se marwi (bayan) hadis mein hai. (aap tashrif le gaey) jabke (abhi) ham 2 siyah cheezein (pani aur khajoor ( bhi pet bhar ke nahi khaatey they."
7457,"Muhammad-bin Ibad aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Marwan fazari ne Yazeed bin kaisaan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! jabke ibne-Ibad ne kaha is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Abu-Hurera ki jaan hai! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi apne ghar walon ko teen din lagaataar gehun ki roti pet bhar kar nahi khilaai thi yahan tak ke aap duniya se tashrif ley gaey."
7458,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne hamein Yazeed bin kaisan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazim ne hadis bayan ki kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kai baar dekha wo ungli se ishara kartey they kehtey they us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Abu-Hurera ki jaan hai! Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke ghar walon ne kabhi lagatar teen din gandam ki roti sair ho kar nahi khaai thi yahan tak ke aap duniya se rukhsat ho gaey."
7459,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein abu-Ahwas ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : kya tum logon ko apni marzi ka khana aur peena muyassar nahi? maine tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha tha aap ke paas raddi khajoor bhi itni nahi hoti thi jis se aap apna pet bhar lein aur Quteba ne ( بہ ( (jis se) ka zikr nahi kya."
7460,Zuhair aur Israel donon ne Samak se isi sanad ke sath usi ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki aur Zuhair ki hadis mein mazeed hai aur tum khajooron aur makkhan ki kai qismon ke baghair razi nahi hotey.
7461,"Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ko khutba detey huey suna, kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is baat ka zikr kya ke logon ne duniya mein se kya kuchh hasil kar liya hai. phir farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha tha aap pura din bhook se laut-tey they aur aapko sukhi hui itni sakht khajoor bhi muyassar na hoti thi jis se apna pet bhar letey."
7462,abu Hani ne abu Abdur-Rehman ko kehtey huey suna : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unse kisi aadmi ne puchha tha : kya ham fuqara muhajireen mein se nahi hain? to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : kya tumhari biwi hai jiske paas tum aaraam karne ke liye jatey ho. usne kaha : haan. puchha : kya tumharey paas rihaaish-gaah hai jahan tum rehtey ho? usne kaha : mere paas to khaadim (bhi) hai kaha : phir to tum baadshaahon mein se ho.
7463,"abu Abdur-Rehman ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas teen shakhs aaey jabke main unke yahaan tha wo kehney lagey : abu-Muhammad! Allah ki qasam! hamein koi cheez muyassar nahi hai na kharch na sawari aur na saman (wo log waaqeatan faqeer they) Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : tum kya chahtey ho? agar tum pasand karo to dobara hamarey paas aao Allah Taala jo tumharey liye muhaiya krega, ham tumhen de dengey. agar chaho to ham tumhara zikr ba-ikhtiyaar Hakim ke paas kar dengey. (wo tumhari zarooraton ka khayal rakhega) aur agar tum chaho to sabr karo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : be-shak hijrat karke aaney waley faqeer qiyamat ke roz maaldaron ki nisbat chalis (40) saal pahley jannat mein jaengey. un (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne kaha : ham sabr karengey. koi cheez nahi maangengey."
7464,Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ashaabe-hijr ke mutaalliq farmaya : un azab diye gaey logon ke yahan (unke gharon mein) dakhil na hona magar is sura mein ke tum ( Allah ke ghazab ke dar se) ro rahe ho. agar tum ro nahi rahe ho to unke yahaan dakhil na hona aisa na ho ke tum par bhi wahi azab aa jaey jo un par aaya tha.
7465,Salim bin-Abdullah ne kaha ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath hijr (qaum Samood ki ujdi hui basti) ke paas se guzrey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : jin logon ne apne aap par zulm kya hai unki rihaaish gahon mein dakhil na hona magar is tarah ke tum ro rahe ho. dar hai ke tumhen bhi wahi azab na aaey jisne unhein aa liya tha phir aap ne zor se sawari ko haanka raftaar tez ki yahan tak ke us jagah ko peechhey chhod diya.
7466,Shuaib bin Ishaq ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se khabar di unhein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (safar karne waale) log sarzamine-Samud Hijr mein utar gaey aur wahan ke kunon se pani hasil kya aur uske sath aata ( bhi) goondh liya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke unhon-ne jo pani bhara hai wo baha dein aur gundha hua aata oonton ko khila dein aur unse kaha : ke wo us kuwein se pani hasil karein jahan (hazrat Saleh (Alaihissalam) ki) ontni pani peeney ke liye aaya karti thi.
7467,"Anas bin ayaaz ne kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne (alfaz ki tabdili se) kaha :  فاستقوا من بئارها واعتجنوا به ( mana mein koi farq nahi. ("
7468,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne Saur bin Zaid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu Ghais se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : bewa aur miskeen ke liye mehnat karne wala Allah ki raah mein jihad karne waley ki tarah hai. aur mera ( Abdullaah-bin-Muslima ka ( khayal hai ke unhon ( Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina ( ne kaha : wo ( Allah ke samney (us qiyam karne waley ki tarah hai jo waqfa karta hai na thaktaa hai aur us rozey daar ki tarah hai jo roza nahi chhorta ."
7469,Ishaq bin Esa ne kaha : hamein Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne Saur bin Yazeed se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Abu Ghais ko Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yateem ki parwarish karne wala uska apna (rishtedar) ho ya ghair ho main aur wo jannat mein is tarah hongey. phir Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne shahadat ki ungli aur darmyani ungli (ko milaakar us) ke sath ishara kya.
7470,"Haaroon-bin-Saeed eili aur Ahmed bin Esa ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein (Abdullah) ibne-Wahab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Haris ne bataya ke Bukair ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhein Aasim bin Umar-bin Qatada ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Ubaidullah Kholani ko bayan kartey huey suna ke unhon-ne Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid ki nai tameer ke waqt logon ne unko baatein kin, suna : (wo keh rahe they) tum logon ne bahut baatein ki hain jabke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna tha : jisne masjid ki tameer ki. Bukair ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon ( Aasim ( ne ye jumla bhi kaha is se wo Allah ki raza chahta hai to Allah uske liye jannat mein us jaisa ( ghar ( banaeyga aur Harun ki riwayat mein hai : Allah Taala uske liye jannat mein ghar banaega."
7471,"Suhak bin Mukhlid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abdul-Hameed bin Jafar ne khabar di kaha : hamein mere walid ne Mehmood-bin Labid se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ne masjid banaaney ka irada kya to logon ne usko na-pasand kya. wo chahtey they ke us (masjid ( ko uski asl haalat par rehney diya jaey to unhon (Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jisne Allah ke liye masjid banai Allah Taala uske liye jannat mein uske jaisa ghar banaega."
7472,Abu-Bakar Hanfi aur Abdul-Malik bin Sabaah donon ne abdul-Hameed bin Jafar se isi sanad ke sath khabar di magar un donon ki hadis mein hai. Allah uske liye jannat mein ghar banaega.
7473,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdul-Azeez bin abu-Salma ne Wahab bin kaisaan se khabar di unhon-ne Ubaid-bin-Umair Lesi se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhone Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : aik baar aik shakhs zamin mein aik sehraai tukdey par khada tha. us ne aik badal mein awaz suni : falan ke baagh ko sairaab karo. wo badal aik taraf hata aur aik pathreeli zamin mein apna pani undel diya. pani ke bahaao wali nadiyon mein se aik nadi ne wo Sara pani apne andar ley liya. wo shakhs pani ke peechhey-peechhey chal pada to wahan aik aadmi apne baagh mein khada apne kudaal se pani ka rukh (apne baagh ki taraf) pher raha hai. us ne us se kaha : Allah ke bandey ! tumhara naam kya hai? usne kaha : falan wahi naam jo usney badal mein suna tha. us ( aadmi ( ne us se kaha : Allah ke bandey ! tum ne mujh se mera naam kyon puchha hai? usne kaha : maine us badal mein, jiska ye pani hai, ( kisi ko) ye kehtey suna tha. falan ke baagh ko sairaab karo tumhara naam liya tha. tum usmein kya kartey ho. us ne jawab diya tum ne ye baat keh di hai to main ( tumhen bata deta hun (us baagh se jo kuchh hasil hota hai main is par nazar daal kar uska aik tehai hissey sadqa kar deta hun aik tehai main aur mere ghar waley khaatey hain. aur aik tehai usi (baagh ki dekh-bhaal) mein laga deta hun."
7474,"Abu-Dawud ne hamein khabar di hamein Abdul-Azeez bin abi Salma ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : hamein Wahab bin kaisan ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki magar unhon-ne (is tarah) kaha : uska aik tehai miskeenon, sawal karne walon aur musaafir ke liye mukhtas kar deta hun."
7475,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne irshad farmaya ke Sharik banaey janey walon mein sabse zyada main sharaakat se mustaghni (beniyaz) hun. jis shakhs ne bhi koi amal kya aur is mein mere sath kisi aur ko Sharik kya to main usey uske shirk ke sath akelaa chhod deta hun.
7476,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs (apna amal logon ko) sunata hai Allah uske barey mein (honey wala faisla) logon ko sunaaeyga (aur usey ruswa karega) aur jo (logon ko) dikhaata phirta hai Allah Taala uske barey mein logon ko dikha dega. (ke iska anjam kya hua.)"
7477,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Salma bin Kuhail se riwayat ki. unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jundub Alaqi (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ( logon ko) sunata hai Allah Taala uske barey mein (sab ko) sunwaaeyga aur jo (apna amal) logon ko dikhaata hai Allah Taala uske barey mein logon ko dikhaaeyga."
7478,"Mulai ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur mazeed kaha : aur main (Salma bin Kuhail) ne (is hadis mein) unke siwa kisi ko (saraahat se) ye kehtey huey nahi suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya."
7479,"Saeed-bin-Umar aur Ashasi ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Waleed-bin-Harab. Saeed ne kaha : mera khayal hai unhon ( Sufiyan ( ne kaha : ( Waleed ( ibne- Haris bin abi Musa . se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Salma bin Kuhail se suna unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ke ilawa aur kisi ko ye kehtey huey nahi suna. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, wo kehtey hain. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna ( aagey ( jis tarah ( Sufiyan ( Sory ki hadis ( 7478 ( mein hai."
7480,"aur yahi hadis hamein ibne-abi-Umar ne bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein sachey amaanatdaar shakhs Waleed bin Harab ne isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki."
7481,Bakr bin Muzar ne ibne-Haad se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se unhon-ne Esa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ( kabhi-kabhi ( banda koi kalima keh deta hai jiski wjah se dozakh mein us se bhi zyada door utar jata hai jitni doori mashriq aur maghrib ke darmyan hai.
7482,"Abdul-Azeez Darawardi ne Yazeed bin haad se unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ibrahim se unhon-ne Esa-bin-Talha se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : banda koi aisa kalima keh deta hai ke usko waazeh taur par pata nahi hota ke usmein kya hai, uski wjah se wo dozakh mein us se zyada door ja girta hai jitni doori mashriq aur maghrib ke darmyan hai."
7483,"abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : ke unse kaha gaya : tum kyon Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ja kar baat nahi kartey ? (ke wo logon ki mukhalifat ka izaala karein ( to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum samajhtey ho ke main tumhen nahi sunwaata to main unse baat nahi karta? Allah ki qasam! maine unse baat ki jo mere aur unke darmyan thi iske baghair ke main kisi aisi baat ki shuruat karun jis mein sabse pahley darwaza kholney wala main banun. main kisi se jo mujh par ameer ho ye nahi kehta ke wo sab insanon mein se behtar hai. is baat ke baad jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi, aap farma rahe they. qiyamat ke din aik aadmi ko laya jaeyga aur aag mein phenk diya jaeyga, uske pet ki antadiyaan bahar nikal padengi. wo unke gird is tarah chakkar lagaey ga jis tarah gadha chakki ke gird lagata hai. ahale-jahannam uske paas jama ho jaeinge aur us se kahengey falan! tumharey sath kya hua? kya to nekiyon ki talqeen aur buraaiyon se mana nahi kya karta tha? wo kahega aisa hi tha, main nekiyon ka hukm deta tha khud (neki ke kaam) nahi karta tha aur buraaiyon se rokta tha aur khud unka irtikaab karta tha."
7484,Jarir ne Aamash se aur unhon-ne abu-Waail se riwayat ki kaha : ham Hazrat Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they ke aik aadmi ne kaha : aapko kya cheez us se rukawat hai ke aap Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jayen aur jo wo kar rahe hain iske barey mein unse baat karein? iske baad usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7485,"Salim ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. meri tamam ummat ko (gunahon par) maafi milegi. siwaey un logon ke jo (apne gunahon ka ( elaan karne waley hain. elaan mein ye hai ke banda raat ko aik kaam karey, phir subah ho to Allah ne iska parda rakha hua ho aur wo khud kahey aey falan ! maine pichhli raat aisa aisaa kaam kya halanke us ne raat guzaar di uske rab ne is par parda daley rakha aur wo subah karta hai to wo apne rab ka daala hua parda khud utaar deta hai. Zuhair ne ( ( اجهار) yani elaan ke bajaey) ( وَإِنَّ مِنَ الھِجَارَ ( (ye badi be-hayaai ki baat hai) kaha."
7486,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Sulaiman Taimi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas 2 aadmiyon ko chheenk aai to aap ne aik aadmi ko chheenk ki dua na di. aap ne jis ko chheenk ki dua na di thi usne kaha : falan ko chheenk aai to aap ne is par usey dua di aur mujhey chheenk aai to aap ne mujhey is par dua na di Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ne alhamdulillah kaha tha aur tum ne alhamdulillah nahi kaha."
7487,"abu-Khalid Ahmar ne Sulaiman Taimi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki."
7488,abu-Burda se riwayat hai kaha : main (apne walid) Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya wo us waqt Hazrat Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ke ghar they. mujhey chheenk aai to unhon-ne jawab mein dua nahi di aur us (fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ( ko chheenk aai to usko unhon-ne jawab mein dua di main apni walida ke paas gaya aur unhein bataya jab wo (mere walid) un (meri walida) ke paas aaey to unhon-ne kaha : tumharey paas mere betey ko chheenk aai to tum ne jawab mein dua nahi di aur un (Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti) ko chheenk aai to tum ne jawab mein dua di. unhon-ne kaha : tumharey betey ko chheenk aai to usne alhamdulillah nahi kaha : isliye maine jawab nahi diya us (khatun) ko chheenk aai to unhon-ne (al-hamdulillah) kaha : isliye maine unko jawab mein dua di. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : aap farmatey they : jab tum mein se kisi ko chheenk aaey aur wo (al-hamdulillah) kahey to usko jawab mein dua do aur agar wo al-hamdulillah na kahey to dua na do.
7489,"Ayas bin Salma-bin-Akwa ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne unse hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : aap ke paas aik shakhs ko chheenk aai to aap ne usey dua di ( يَرْحَمُكَ اللَّهُ ( Allah tum par raham farmaai . usey dusri chheenk aai to aap ne farmaya us shakhs ko zukaam hai."
7490,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jamaai shaitan ki taraf se hai lihaza tum mein se jab kisi shakhs ko jamaai aaey to wo jahan tak usko rok sakey rokey.
7491,Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne kaha : hamein Suhel bin abi-Saleh ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey (Abdur-Rehman) se suna wo mere walid ko apne walid se hadis bayan kar rahe they unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko jamaai aaey to wo apne munh par hath rakh kar usko rokey kyonke (aisa na karne se) shaitan andar dakhil hota hai.
7492,Abdul-Azeez ne Suhel se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi ko jamaai aaey to wo usey apne hath se rokey kyonke shaitan andar dakhil hota hai.
7493,"Sufiyan ne Suhel bin abi Saleh se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko Namaz mein jamaai aaey to wo jitna iske bas mein ho usko rokey kyonke shaitan andar dakhil hota hai."
7494,"Jarir ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid aur Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, (aagey) Bishr aur Abdul-Azeez ki hadis ki tarah."
7495,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : farishton ko noor se paida kya gaya hai aur jinon ko aag ke sholey se aur Adam (Alaihissalam) ko us (maaddey) se paida kya gaya hai jis ko tumharey liye bayan kya gaya hai."
7496,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim, Muhammad-bin-Musanna Anzi aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah razi ne hamein Saqafi se hadis bayan ki, alfaz ibne-Musanna ke hain. kaha : hamein abdul-Wahaab ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Khalid ne Muhammad-bin-Sirin se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Bani-Israeel ki aik ummat gum ho gaee thi, malum nahi ke wo kahan hai aur mujhey iske siwa aur koi baat nazar nahi aai ke wo log (yahi) choohey hain. ( unhon-ne maskh hokar ye shakl ikhtiyar kar li hai) tum dekhtey nahi ke jab unke samney ontni ka doodh rakha jaey to (Bani-Israeel ki tarah) wo usko nahi peetey. agar unke liye bakri ka doodh rakha jaey to wo usey pi letey hain. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine ye hadis Kab ( ahbaar) ko sunai to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha? maine kaha : haan. unhon-ne baar-baar yahi kaha to maine kaha : (nahi to) kya main Taurait padhta hun (ke wahan se bayan karunga?) Ishaq ne apni riwayat mein kaha : ham nahi jantey unka kya bana?"
7497,"Hisham ne Muhammad (bin Sirin) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : chuhiya maskh-shuda hai aur uski daleel ye hai ke uske samney bakri ka doodh rakha jaey to ye pi leti hai aur uske samney ontni ka doodh rakha jaey to ye usko munh tak nahi lagaati. to Kab ( ahbaar ( ne unse kaha : aap ne ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi? Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to kya mujh par Taurait nazil hui thi?"
7498,"Aqeel ne Zohri se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin aik suraakh se 2 martaba nahi dasaa jata."
7499,"ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ne apne chacha se, unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
7500,"Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : momin ka mamla ajeeb hai. iska har maamla uske liye bhalai ka hai. aur ye baat momin ke siwa kisi aur ko muyassar nahi. usey khushi aur khush-hali miley to shukr karta hai. aur ye uske liye achchha hota hai aur agar usey koi nuqsan pahunchey to ( Allah ki raza ke liye) sabr karta hai, ye ( abhi ( uske liye bhalai hoti hai."
7501,"Yazid bin Zure ne Khalid Haza se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Bakra se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik aadmi ne doosrey aadmi ki tareef ki, kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par afsos hai! tum ne apne sathi ki gardan kaat di, apne sathi ki gardan kaat di. kai baar kaha : (phir farmaya :) tum mein se kisi shakhs ne laa-muhaala apne sathi ki tareef karni ho to is tarah kahey : main falan ko aisa samajhta hun, asliyat ko jaanney wala Allah hai. aur main Allah (ke ilm (ke muqaabley mein kisi ki khoobi bayan nahi kar raha, mein usey (aisa) samajhta hun. agar wo waqei us khoobi ko janta hai (to kahey!). wo is tarah (ki khoobi rakhta) hai."
7502,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Khalid Haza se, hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi bakra se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik aadmi ka zikr hua to aik shakhs kehney laga : Allah ke rasool! koi aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad falan-falan baat mein us ( aadmi ( se afzal nahi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum par afsos! tum ne apne sathi ki gardan kaat di. aap baar-baar ye kehtey rahe, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum mein se kisi ne la muhaala apne bhai ki tareef karni ho to is tarah kahey : main samajhta hun falan (is tarah hai) agar wo waqei usko aisa samajhta ho (phir kahey) aur main Allah (ke ilm) ke muqaabley mein kisi ki khoobi bayan nahi karta (jis se ye Sabit ho ke main نعوذباللہ , Allah ke ilm ko jhutlaa raha hun.)"
7503,"Hashim bin-Qasim aur Shababa bin Sawwar donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath Yazeed bin Zure ki hadis ki tarah bayan kya, un donon ki riwayaton mein ye nahi ke us shakhs ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad koi shakhs us ( aadmi ( se afzal nahi."
7504,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ‌ se riwayat hai, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko suna, wo kisi aadmi ki tareef kar raha tha, tareef mein usey bahut badha-chadha raha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum logon ne usko halaak kar daala ya (farmaya :) tum logon ne us aadmi ki kamr tod di."
7505,"abu Mamar se riwayat hai ke aik shakhs khada hua umra mein se kisi ameer ki tareef karne laga to Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) us shakhs par mitti dalney lagey, aur kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein ye hukm diya tha ke ham madah saraaon ke munh mein mitti daalein."
7506,"Shoba ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim (bin Yazeed Nakhai ( se, unhon-ne Hammam bin-Haaris se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki tareef karne laga to Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska rukh kya, apne ghutnon par baithey, wo bhari bharkam ( jism ke Malik ( they aur us aadmi ke chehrey par kankariyaan phainkney lagey. Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : aap kya kar rahe hain? unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jab tum madah saraaon ko dekho to unke chehron mein mitti dalo."
7507,"Sufiyan Sory ne Mansoor aur Aamash se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Hammam se, unhon-ne Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi (hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki."
7508,"Naafe se riwayat hai, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maine khuwab mein dekha ke main miswak kar raha hun, 2 aadmiyon ne mujhey apni apni taraf kheencha, unmein se aik doosrey se bada tha, maine miswak chhotey ko pakda di to mujh se kaha gaya : badey ko dein, chunanche maine wo badey ke hawale kar di."
7509,"Hisham ne apne walid (Urwa) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) hadisein bayan kar rahe they aur awaz laga rahe they : aey hujrey ki maalika! suniye, aey hujrey ki maalika! suniye, us waqt Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (andar) Namaz padh rahi thin. unhon-ne jab Namaz mukammal ki to Urwa se kaha : tum ne abhi usey aur uski kahi hui baat nahi suni? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik waqt mein) aik baat (hadis) irshad farmatey they, agar koi ginney wala usey ginta to gin sakta tha."
7510,"Haddab bin Khalid azdi ne kaha : hamein Hammam ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujh se ( suni hui baatein ( mat likho, jisne Quran Majeed (ke sath us) ke ilawa meri koi baat (hadis) likhi wo usko mitaa de, albatta meri hadis (yaad rakh kar aagey) bayan karo, usmein koi harj nahi, aur jisne mujh par. Hammam ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke unhon ( Zaid-bin-Aslam ( ne kaha : jaan-bojh kar jhoot baandha wo ا apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley."
7511,"saiyedna Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum se pahley logon mein aik badshah tha aur iska aik jadoo gar tha. jab wo jadoo gar boodha ho gaya to badshah se bola ke main boodha ho gaya hun, mere paas koi ladka bhej ke main usko jaadoo sikhlaaoon. badshah ne uske paas aik ladka bheja, wo usko jaadoo sikhlaataa tha. us ladkey ki aamad-o-raft (aane-jane) ki raah mein aik raahib tha (isai darwesh yani paadri taarik), wo ladka uske paas betha aur uska kalam suna to usey uski baatein achi lagin. ab jadoo gar ke paas jata to raahib ki taraf se ho kar nikalta aur uske paas baithtaa , phir jab jadoo gar ke paas jata to jadoo gar usko (der se aaney ki wjah se) maarta. aakhir ladkey ne jadoo gar ke maarney ka raahib se gilla kiya to raahib ne kaha ke jab to jadoo gar se darey , to ye keh diya kar ke mere ghar walon ne mujh ko rok rakha tha aur jab to apne ghar walon se darey, to keh diya kar ke jadoo gar ne mujhey rok rakha tha. usi haalat mein wo ladka raha ke achcha aik badey darindey par guzra ke jisne logon ko aamad-o-raft (aane-jane) se rok rakha tha. ladkey ne kaha ke aaj main malum karta hun ke jadoo gar afzal hai ya raahib afzal hai. us ne aik patthar liya aur kaha ke ilahi agar raahib ka tariqa tujhey jadoo gar ke tareeqey se zyada pasand ho, to is janwar ko qatl kar taake log guzar jaaein. phir usko patthar se maara to wo janwar mar gaya aur log guzarney lagey. phir wo ladka raahib ke paas aaya us se ye haal kaha to wo bola ke betaa to mujh se badh gaya hai. yaqinan tera rutba yahan tak pahuncha jo main dekhta hun aur to an-qareeb aazmaya jaeyga phir agar to aazmaya jaey to mera naam na batlaanaa. us ladkey ka ye haal tha ke andhey aur kodhi ko achchha karta aur har qism ki bimari ka ilaaj karta tha. ye haal jab badshah ke masaahib (darbari) jo ke andha ho gaya tha suna to us ladkey ke paas bahut se tohfey laya aur kehney laga ke ye sab maal tera hai agar to mujhey achchha kar de. ladkey ne kaha ke main kisi ko achchha nahi karta, achchha karna to Allah Taala ka kaam hai, agar to Allah par imaan laye to main Allah se dua karunga to wo tujhey achchha kar dega. wo wazeer Allah par imaan laya to Allah ne usko achchha kar diya. wo badshah ke paas gaya aur uske paas betha jaisa ke betha karta tha. badshah ne kaha ke teri aankhen kis ne roshan ki? wazeer bola ke mere Malik ne. badshah ne kaha ke mere siwa tera Malik kon hai? wzeer ne kaha ke mera aur tera Malik Allah hai. badshah ne usko pakda aur azab dena shuru kiya, yahan tak ke usne ladkey ka naam ley liya. wo ladka bulaya gaya. badshah ne us se kaha ke aey betaa to jaadoo mein is darje par pahuncha ke andhey aur kodhi ko achchha karta hai aur badey badey kaam karta hai? wo bola ke main to kisi ko achchha nahi karta balke Allah achchha karta hai. badshah ne usko pakda aur maarta raha, yahan tak ke usne raahib ka naam batlaya. raahib pakad liya gaya. us se kaha gaya ke apne Deen se phir jaa. uske na manney par badshah ne aik aara mangwaya aur raahib ki maang par rakh kar usko cheer daala, yahan tak ke do tukdey ho kar gir padaa. phir wo wzeer bulaya gaya, us se kaha gaya ke to apne Deen se phir ja , usne bhi na maanaa uski maang par bhi aara rakha gaya aur cheer daala yahan tak ke do tukdey ho kar gir padaa. phir wo ladka bulaya gaya, us se kaha ke apne Deen se palat ja , usne bhi inkar kiya. badshah ne usko apne chand sathiyon ke hawale kiya aur kaha ke usko falan pahaad par ley ja kar choti par chadhaao , jab tum choti par pahuncho to is ladkey se poochho, agar wo apne Deen se phir jaey to khair , nahi to isko dhakel do. wo isko le gaey aur pahaad par chadhaayaa . ladkey ne dua ki ke ilahi jis tarah to chahey mujhey inke shar se bacha. pahaad hilaa aur wo log gir padey. wo ladka badshah ke paas chala aaya. badshah ne puchha ke terey sathi kahan gaey? usne kaha ke Allah ne mujhey unke shar se bacha liya. phir badshah ne usko apne chand sathiyon ke hawale kiya aur kaha ke isko aik kashti mein dariya ke andar ley jao, agar apne Deen se phir jaey to khair , warna isko dariya mein dhakel dena. wo log isko ley gaey. ladkey ne kaha ke ilahi ! to mujhey jis tarah chahey inke shar se bacha ley. wo kashti aundhi ho gaee aur ladkey ke siwa sab sathi doob gaey aur ladka zinda bach kar badshah ke paas aa gaya. badshah ne us se puchha ke terey sathi kahan gaey? wo bola ke Allah Taala ne mujhey unke shar se bacha liya. phir ladkey ne badshah se kaha ke to mujhey us waqt tak na mar sakega , jab tak ke jo tariqa main bataun wo na kare. badshah ne kaha ke wo kya? usne kaha ke to sab logon ko aik maidan mein jama karke mujhey aik lakdi par sooli de, phir mere tarkash se aik teer lekar kamaan ke andar rakh, phir keh ke us Allah ke naam se maarta hun jo us ladkey ka Malik hai. phir teer mar. agar to aisa karega to mujhey qatl karega. badshah ne sab logon ko aik maidan mein jama kiya, us ladkey ko darakht ke taney par latkaayaa , phir uske tarkash mein se aik teer liya aur teer ko kamaan ke andar rakh kar ye kehtey huey maara ke Allah ke naam se maarta hun jo is ladkey ka Malik hai. wo teer ladkey ki kanpati par laga. us ne apna hath teer ke maqam par rakha aur mar gaya. logon ne ye haal dekh kar kaha ke ham to is ladkey ke Malik par imaan laaey, ham is ladkey ke Malik par imaan laaey, ham is ladkey ke Malik par imaan laaey. kisi ne badshah se kaha ke Allah ki qism ! jis se to darta tha wahi hua yani log imaan ley aaey. badshah ne raston ke naalon par khandaqein khodney ka hukm diya. phir khandaqein khodi gain aur unmein khub aag bhadkaai gaee aur kaha ke jo shakhs is Deen se (yani ladkey ke Deen se) na phirey , usey in khandaqon mein dhakel do, ya us se kaha jaey ke in khandaqon mein girey. logon ne aisa hi kiya, yahan tak ke aik aurat aai jiske sath uska bachcha bhi tha, is aurat ne aag mein girney se tardeed (sankoch) kiya to bachchey ne kaha ke aey maan ! sabr kar to sachey Deen par hai."
7512,"Harun-bin-Maruf aur Muhammad-bin-Ibad ne hamein hadis bayan ki, alfaz donon se miltey-jultey hain jabke siyaaq (sandarbh) Harun ka hai. donon ne kaha : hamein Hatim-bin-Ismail ne Yaqoob-bin-Mujahid-abu-Hazra se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ubada-bin-Waleed-bin-Ubada-bin-Samit se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur mere walid ilm hasil karne ke liye Ansar ke is qabeeley ki halaakat se pahley usmein gaey, sabse pahley shakhs jin se hamari mulaqat hui wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Hazrat abu-yusr (Raziallahu anhu) they, unke sath unka aik ghulam bhi tha jiske paas sahaaif ( dastaawez (ka aik majmooa tha, Hazrat abu-yusr (Raziallahu anhu) ke badan par aik dhaari-daar chadar aur muaafiri ka bana hua aik kapda tha aur unke ghulam ke jism par bhi aik dhaari-daar chadar aur aik muaafiri kapda tha. mere walid ne unse kaha : chacha ! main ghussey ki bina par aap ke chehrey par rang ki tabdili dekh raha hun, unhon-ne kaha : haan , falan-bin-falan , jis ka taalluq banu-haram se hai, ke zimmey mera maal tha, main uske ghar walon ke yahan gaya, salam kiya aur maine puchha : kya wo hai? ghar walon ne kaha : nahi hai phir achcha uska aik kam umr ladka mere samney ghar se nikla , maine us se puchha : teera bap kahan hai? usne kaha : unhon-ne aap ki awaz suni to wo meri walida ke chhappar khat mein ghus gaey hain. maine kaha : nikal kar meri taraf aa jao, mujhey pata chal gaya hai ke tum kahan ho. wo bahar nikal aaya maine puchha : is baat ka baais kya bana ke tum mujh se chhup gaey? usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main aapko bataata hun aur main aap se jhoot nahi boloon ga , Allah ki qism ! main is baat se dara ke kahin mein aap se baat karun aur jhoot boloon aur main aap se wada karun aur aap ke sath uski khilaf warzi karun. jabke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi hain aur Allah ki qism main tang dast tha. unhon-ne kaha ke maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine ( dobara ( kaha : Allah ki qism ! usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! maine ( phir ( kaha : Allah ki qism ! usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! kaha : phir unhon-ne apna saheefa (jis par qarz ki tahreer likhi hui thi) nikala aur apne hath se usko mitaa diya ( phir maqrooz se) kaha : agar tumhen adaaeygi ke liye maal mil jaey to mera qarz lota dena aur nahi to tum bari-uzzimma ho, main gawahi deta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko meri un donon aankhon ki basaarat ne (dekha) aur (ye kehtey huey) unhon-ne apni do ungliyan apni do aankhon par rakhin , aur mere in donon kanon ne suna aur mere is dil ne yad rakha aur unhon-ne apne dil wali jagah par ishara kiya. jabke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : jis shakhs ne kisi tang dast ko mohlat di ya uska qarz khatm kar diya Allah Taala apne saaey se is par saaya karega ."
7513,"(Ubada-bin-Waleed ne) kaha : maine unse kaha : chacha jaan ! agar aap apne ghulam ki dhaari-daar chadar ley letey aur usey apna muaafiri kapda de detey ya us se uska muaafiri kapda ley letey aur usey apni dhaari-daar chadar de detey to aap ke jism par aik joda hota aur uske jism par bhi aik joda hota. unhon-ne mere sar par hath phera aur kaha : aey Allah ! isko barkat ata farmaa. bhatijey ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko meri aankhon ki basaarat (ne dekha) aur mere do kanon ne suna aur. dil ke maqam ki taraf ishara kartey huey kaha mere dil ne usey yad rakha , jabke aap farma rahe they. un (ghulaamon) ko usi mein se khilaao jo tum khaatey ho aur usi mein se pahnaao jo tum pahntey ho. agar maine usey duniya ki ne'maton mein se (uska hissa) de diya hai to ye mere liye us se zyada aasan hai ke wo qiyamat ke roz meri nekiyan ley jata."
7514,"phir ham (aagey) rawaana huey yahan tak ke ham Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas unki masjid mein hazir huey wo aik kapdey mein usey donon palluon ko mukhalif simton mein kandhon ke uper se guzaar kar baandhey huey Namaz padh rahe they. main logon ko phalaangtaa hua gaya yahan tak ke unke aur qibley ke darmyan ja kar baith gaya. (jab wo Namaz se farigh huey to) maine unse kaha : aap aik kapdey mein Namaz padh rahe hain aur aap ki chadar aap ke pahlu mein padi hui hai? unhon-ne is tarah apne hath se mere seeney mein maara unhon (Ubada) ne apni ungliyan alag kin aur unhein kamaan ki tarah modaa (aur kehney lagey) main (yahi) chahta tha ke tum jaisa koi naa-samajh mere paas aaey aur dekhey ke main kya kar raha hun, phir wo (bhi) is tarah kar liya kare. (phir kaha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari is masjid mein tashrif laey aap ke hath mein ibne-taab (ki khajoor ( ki aik shaakh thi aap ne masjid ke qibley ki taraf (wali diwar par) jama hua balgham laga dekha. aap ne khajoor ki shaakh se usko khurch kar saaf kiya phir hamari taraf rukh karke farmaya : tum mein se kon pasand karta hai ke Allah Taala us se ea'raaz (bachey) farmaai (uski taraf nazar tak na karey? ( kaha : to ham sab dar gaey. aap ne phir farmaya : tum mein se kon ye pasand karta hai ke Allah Taala us se bachey? kaha : ham par khof taari ho gaya aap ne phir se farmaya : tum mein se kisey ye baat achchhi lagti hai ke Allah Taala us se ea'raaz farmaey? ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke rasool ! ham mein se kisi ko bhi (ye baat pasand) nahi aap ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs jab Namaz ke liye khada hota hai to Allah tabarak w taala uske samney ki taraf hota hai lihaza usey samney ki taraf hargiz thookna nahi chahiye na daain taraf hi thookna chahiye apni baain taraf baain paon ke nichey thookey. agar jaldi nikalney wali ho to apne kapdey ke sath is tarah (saaf) kare. phir aap ne kapdey ke aik hissey ki doosrey hissey par teh lagai phir farmaya : mujhey khushbu laakar do. qabeeley ka aik naujawaan uth kar apne ghar walon ki taraf bhaagaa aur apni hatheli mein khushbu ley gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo (khushbu) li usey chhadi ke sirey par lagaya aur jis jagah sookhaa balgham laga hua tha is par mal di. Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : yahan se tum ne apni masjidon mein khushbu lagaani shuru ki."
7515,"(Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wadi bawaat ki jang mein they. aap (qabeela juhaina ke sardaar) majdi-bin-Amr-Juhni ko dhoond rahe they pani dhoney waley aik oont par ham panch (5), chh (6), aur saat (7) aadmi baari-baari baithtey they. Ansar mein se aik aadmi ki apne oont par (baithney ki) baari aai to usne oont ko bithaya aur is par Sawar ho gaya. phir usko uthaya to us (oont ( ne us (ke hukm) par uthney mein kisi had tak der ki to usne kaha : khada ho, tum par Allah laanat kare. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye apne oont par laanat karne wala kon hai? usne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! main. aap ne farmaya is se utar jao jis par laanat ki gaee ho wo hamarey sath na chaley apne aapko baddua na do na apni aulad ko baddua do na apne maal maweshi ko baddua do Allah ki taraf se (muqarrar karda qabooliyat ki) ghadi ki muwafiqat (barabari) na karo jis mein (jo) kuchh maanga jata hai wo tumhen ata kar diya jata hai."
7516,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath rawaana huey yahan tak ke jab kisi had tak Sham ho gaee aur ham Arab ke paaniyon mein se kisi pani ke qareeb pahunchey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kon shakhs hai jo ham se pahley ja kar hauz (ke kinarey ko mazbut karne ke liye us) ki lipaai karega aur khud bhi pani piye ga aur hamein bhi pilaaey ga? Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main khada ho gaya aur arz ki. Allah ke rasool ! ye hai wo aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kon shakhs Jaabir ke sath jaeyga? to Hazrat jabbaar-bin-sakhr (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey ham kuwein ke paas gaey aur ham ne ( kuwein se nikal kar) hauz mein aik ya do dol pani daley phir usko mitti se leepaa , baad iske usmein pani bharnaa shuru kiya yahan tak ke labaalab bhar diya. sabse pahley ham ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dikhlai diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum donon shakhs ijazat detey ho (mujh ko pani pilaaney ki apne janwar ko)?'' ham ne arz kiya : haan , ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ontni ko chhoda , us ne pani piyaa , phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski baag kheenchi us ne pani peenaa mauqoof (multawi) kiya aur peshab kiya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko alag le gaey aur bitha diya. baad iske Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hauz ki taraf aaey aur wuzu kiya phir main khada hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu karne ki jagah se (pani lekar) wuzu kiya. jabbaar-ban-sakhr (Raziallahu anhu) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye chaley gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhney ke liye khadey ho gaey aur mere jism par aik chadar thi. main (eik taraf ( gaya ke is (chadar) ke donon kinaron ko mukhalif simton mein) kandhon par) daalun to wo mujhey poori na aai. iski jhalrein thin maine is (chadar) ko ulat kar iske kinarey badley phir is par apni gardan se zor daala ( gardan jhukaa kar usey iske nichey dabaayaa ( phir aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baain taraf khada ho gaya. aap ne mere hath se pakad kar mujhey ghumaayaa yahan tak ke mujhey apni daain taraf khada kiya phir jabbaar sakhr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey unhon-ne wuzu kiya aur aa kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baain taraf khadey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham donon ke hath pakdey aur hamein dhakel kar apne peechhey khada kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lagatar meri taraf dekh rahe they aur mujhey pata nahi chal raha tha phir mujhey samajh aai to aap ne hath se is tarah ishara farmaya : aap ka maqsad tha ke apni kamar baandh lo. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (namaz se) farigh huey to farmaya : aey Jaabir ! maine kaha hazir hun Allah ke rasool ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab kapda khula ho to iske kinaron ko mukhalifat simton mein ley jao aur agar tang ho to usko kamar ke uper baandh lo."
7517,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (eik muhim par) gaey. ham mein se har shakhs ki khuraak roz ki aik khajoor thi wo us khajoor ko choostaa rehta aur phir usko apne kapdey mein lapet leta ham apni kamaanon se darakhton ke patey jhaadtey they aur khaatey they yahan tak ke hamari baachhon mein zakhm huey. qism khata hun ke aik din ham mein se aik ghalati se us (eik khajoor ( se mahroom reh gaya ham usey ( sahara de kar) uthatey huey lekar (taqseem karne waley ke paas) gaey aur uske haq mein gawahi di ke usey wo (eik khajoor ( nahi di gaee. wo usey di gaee to usne khud khadey ho kar li.
7518,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (eik muhim ke liye) rawaana huey yahan tak ke ham kushaada wadi mein ja utrey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye gaey main ( chamdey ka bana hua (pani ka aik bartan lekar aap ke peechhey gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nazar daudai aisi cheez nazar na aai jiski aap oat ley saktey. wadi ke kinarey par do darakht nazar aaey aap unmein se aik darakht ke paas tashrif le gaey uski tahniyon mein se aik ko pakada aur farmaya : Allah ke hukm se mere mutee' ho jao . to wo nakel daley huey oont ki tarah aap ka farmaanbardaar bin gaya phir doosrey darakht ke paas aaey aur uski tahniyon mein se aik ko pakda aur kaha : Allah ke hukm se mere mutee' ho jao. to wo bhi isi tarah aap ke sath chal padaa yahan tak ke) usey chalaatey huey) donon ke darmyan ke aadhey faasley par pahunchey to aap ne un donon ko jhukaa kar aapas mein mila (kar ikattha kar) diya aap ne farmaya : donon Allah ke hukm se mere aagey mil jao. to wo donon sath mil gaey (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko parda muhaiya kar diyaa) Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main dar se bhaagta hua wahan se nikla ke mere qareeb honey ko mehsus karke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se ( mazeed ( door) janey par majbur ( na ho jayen aur Muhammad-bin-Ibad ne (apni riwayat mein) kaha : aapko door janey ki zahmat karni padey main (eik jagah ( baith gaya aur apne aap se baatein karne laga. achcha meri nigaah padi to maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la rahe hain aur dekha ke donon darakht alag-alag ho chukey hain. har aik darakht taney par seedha khada ho gaya hai phir maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik baar rukey aur apne sar Mubarak se is tarah ishara kiya. abu Ismail ( Hatim-bin-Ismail ( ne apne sar se daain baain ishara kiya. phir aap aagey tashrif laey jab mere paas pahunchey to farmaya : Jaabir ! kya tum ne mere khadey honey ki jagah dekhi thi? maine kaha ji haan. aap ne farmaya : donon darakhton ki taraf jao aur donon mein se har aik se aik (aik ( shaakh kaat lao yahan tak ke aa kar jab meri jagah par khadey ho jao to aik shaakh apni daain taraf daal dena aur aik shaakh baain taraf . Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main utha aik patthar uthaya usey todaa aur usey ghusaayaa jab wo mere ( kaam ke) ke liye tez ho gaya to un donon darakhton ki taraf aaya har aik se aik (aik) shaakh kaati, phir unko ghaseet'taa hua aaya, yahan tak ke aa kar us jagah khada hua jahan pahley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey they, to aik shaakh apni daain taraf daal di aur aik apni baain taraf . phir main aap ke sath ja mila aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! (jo aap ne farmaya tha) maine kar diya hai wo kis liye tha? farmaya : main do qabron ke paas se guzra unko azab diya ja raha tha. maine unke barey mein shafaat karni chahi ke unse us waqt tak ke liye kami kar di jaey jab tak ye shakhein geeli rahen."
7519,"(hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir ham lashkar ke paas aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya : Jaabir ! wuzu ke pani ke liye awaz do. to maine (har jagah pukar kar) kaha : kya wuzu ka pani nahi hai? kya wuzu ka pani nahi hai? kya wuzu ka pani nahi hai? kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey qafley mein aik qatra (pani) nahi mila. Ansar mein se aik aadmi tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye apne puraaney mishkeezey mein pani daal kar usey khajoor ki tahni (se bani hui ( khoonti se latkaa kar thanda kiya karta tha. (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : aap ne mujh se farmaya falan-bin-falan Ansari ke paas jao aur dekho uske puraaney mishkeezey mein kuchh hai? kaha : main gaya, iske andar dekha to mujhey us (mishkeezey) ke munh wali jagah par aik qatrey ke siwa kuchh nazar na aaya. agar main usey (doosrey bartan mein) nikaaltaa to uska khushk hissey usey pi leta . main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mujhey us ( mishkeezey (ke munh mein pani ke aik qatrey ke siwa kuchh nahi mila. agar main usey undeloon to uska khushk hissey usey pi lega . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jao usey mere paas ley aao . main usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley aaya. aap ne usey hath mein pakda aur kuchh kehna shuru kiya mujhey pata na chala ke aap ne kya kaha aur us ( mishkeezey ( ko apne donon hathon mein dabaaney aur harkat dene lagey, phir aap ne mujhey wo de diya to farmaya : Jaabir ! pani ( pilaaney (ka bada bartan mangwaao . maine awaz di : sawaaron ka bada bartan (tab) laao. usey utha kar mere paas laya gaya to maine usey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakh diya, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna Mubarak hath pyaley mein is tarah kiya, usey phailaayaa aur apni ungliyaan alag-alag kin phir usey bartan ki tahiya mein rakha aur farmaya : Jaabir ! mere hath par pani undel do aur bismillaah padho ! maine usey aap (ke hath ( par undela aur kaha : bismillaah . maine pani ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan se phoot'tey huey dekha, phir wo bada bartan (pani ke josh se) zor se umadney aur ghoomney laga. yahan tak ke pura bhar gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jaabir ! jis-jis ko pani ki zarurat hai usey awaz do. kaha : log aaey aur pani liya, yahan tak ke sab ki zarurat poori ho gaee, kaha : maine elaan kiya koi baqi hai jisey (pani ki) zarurat ho? phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bartan se apna hath uthaya to wo (usi tarah) bharaa hua tha."
7520,"aur logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhook ki shikayat ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : an-qareeb Allah Taala tumhen khana dega. phir ham samandar ke kinarey pahunchey, samandar ne josh maara (eik lahar si aai (aur us ne aik samandari janwar (bahar) phenk diya, ham ne samandar ke kinarey par aag jalaai aur us (ke gosht ( ko pakaya , bhoona , khaya aur sair ho gaey Hazrat Jaabir ne kaha : main aur falan aur falan , unhon-ne panch aadmi giney , uski aankh ke goshey mein ghus gaey to koi hamein dekh nahi sakta tha yahan tak ke ham bahar nikal aaey aur ham ne uski pasliyon mein se aik pasli (aik taraf aik bada kaantaa ( lekar usko kamaan ki haiyat (halat) mein khada kar diya, phir qafley mein sabse badey (qad ke) aadmi ko bulaya aur qafley mein sabse badey oont ko aur qafley ke sabse badey paalaan ko mangwaya , wo shakhs sar jhukaaye baghair us pasli ke nichey dakhil ho gaya."
7521,"Abu-Ishaq ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : Hazrat Abu-Bakar Siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) mere walid ke paas unke ghar aaey aur unse aik kajaawa khareedaa , phir (mere walid) Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey : apne betey ko mere sath bhej dein, wo us (kajaawey) ko mere sath utha kar mere ghar pahuncha de. mere walid ne mujh se kaha : usey tum utha lo to maine usey utha liya aur mere walid uski qeemat leney ke liye unke sath nikal padey. mere walid ne unse kaha : Abu-Bakar ! mujhey ye bataein ke jis raat aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (hijrat ke liye) nikley to aap donon ne kya kiya? unhon-ne kaha : haan ham poori raat chaltey  rahe yahan tak ke do-pahar ka waqt ho gaya aur (dhoop ki shiddat se) rasta khali ho gaya, usmein koi bhi nahi chal raha tha, achcha aik lambi chattaan hamarey samney buland hui, uska saaya bhi tha, is par abhi dhoop nahi aai thi. ham uske paas (sawaariyon se) utar gaey. mein chattaan ke paas aaya, aik jagah apne hath se sanwaari taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske saaey mein so jayen, phir maine aap ke liye us jagah par aik narm khaal bichhaa di, phir kaha : Allah ke rasool ! so jaaiye aur main aap ke ird-gird (ke ilaaqey) ki talashi leta hun (aur nigahbaani karta hun) aap so gaey, mein charon taraf nigrani karne laga to maine dekha aik charwaha apni bakriyan liye chattaan ki taraf aa raha tha. wo bhi iske paas isi tarah (aaram) karna chahta tha jis tarah ham chahtey they. main us se mila aur us se puchha : ladkey ! tum kis ke (ghulam) ho? usne kaha : Madina ke aik shakhs kaa. maine kaha : kya tumhari bakriyon (ke thanon) mein doodh hai? usne kaha : haan. maine kaha : kya tum mere liye doodh nikaalo gey ? usne kaha : haan. us ne aik bakri ko pakda to maine us se kaha : thanon se baal , mitti aur tinkey jhaad lo. ( Abu-Ishaq ne) kaha : thanon se baal mitti aur tinkey jhaad lo. ( Abu-Ishaq ne) kaha : maine Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha wo apna aik hath doosrey par mar kar jhaad rahe they, chunanche us ne mere liye lakdi ke aik pyaley mein thoda sa doodh nikal diya (hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : mere sath chamdey ka aik bartan (bhi) tha, main usmein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pani bhar kar rakhta tha taake aap nosh farmaein aur wuzu karein. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur mujhey ye baat pasand na thi ke aapko jagaaoon, lekin main pahuncha to aap jaag chukey they. maine doodh par kuchh pani daala, yahan tak ke iske nichey ka hissa bhi thanda ho gaya to maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! ye doodh nosh farma lein. aap ne nosh farmaya, yahan tak ke main razi ho gaya. phir aap ne farmaya : kya chalney ka waqt nahi aaya? maine kaha : kyon nahi ! kaha : phir suraj dhal janey ke baad ham rawaana ho gaey aur suraaqa-bin-Malik hamarey peechhey aa gaya, jabke ham aik sakht zamin mein (chal rahe) they. maine kaha : hamein liya gaya hai, aap ne farmaya : gham na karo Allah hamarey sath hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske khilaf dua ki to uske ghodey ki taangein pet tak zamin mein dhans gain. mera khayal hai. usne kaha : mujhey pata chal gaya hai tum donon ne mere khilaf dua ki hai. mere haq mein dua karo. (meri taraf se) tumharey liye Allah zaamin (zamanet dene wala) hai ke main dhoondney walon ko tumhari taraf se lautaaoon ga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye dua ki to wo bach gaya, phir wo laut gaya. jis (peechhaa karne waale) ko milta us se ye kehta : main ( talash kar chuka hun) tumhari taraf se bhi kifaayat karta hun, wo is taraf nahi hain wo jis kisi ko bhi milta usey lota deta. (hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : unhon-ne hamarey sath wafaa ki."
7522,"Zuhair-bin-Harab ne mujhey yahi hadis Usman-bin-Umar se bayan ki, isi ke saath hamein Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne yahi hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Nazar-bin-Shumail ne khabar di, un donon (Usman aur nazar) ne Israel se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Abu-Ishaq se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mere walid se teraah (13) dirham mein aik kajaawaa khareedaa. phir Zuhair ki Abu-Ishaq se riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur apni hadis mein unhon-ne kaha : Usman-bin-Umar ki riwayat mein hai, jab wo (suraaqa (Raziallahu anhu)) qareeb aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke khilaf dua ki, unke ghodey ki taangein pet tak zamin mein dhans gain. wo uchhal kar us se utrey aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! mujhey ye pata chal gaya hai ke ye aap ka kaam hai. aap Allah se dua karein ke wo mujhey is mushkil se, main jis mein phans gaya hun, chhutkaara ata kar de aur aap ki taraf se ye baat mere zimmey hui ke mere peechhey jo bhi (aap ka ta'aqub (peechha) kar raha) hai main uski aankhon ko (aap ki taraf ( dekhney se rok doonga aur ye mera tarkash hai, usmein se aik teer nikal lein, aap falan maqam par mere oonton aur mere ghulaamon ke paas se guzrengey , unmein se jiski zarurat ho usey ley lein. aap ne farmaya : mujhey tumharey oonton ki zarurat nahi. chunanche ham raat ke waqt Madina (ke qareeb) pahunchey. logon ne iske barey mein tanaaza' (jhagda) kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis ke yahan utrein gey (mehman banengey) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main (apne dada) abdul-Muttalib ke nanihaal banu-Najjaar ka mehman bin kar unki izzat afzaai karunga. mard , auratein gharon ke uper chadh gaey aur ghulam aur naukar-chaakar raston mein bikhar gaey. wo pukar-pukaar kar keh rahe they : aey Muhammad ! aey Allah ke rasool ! (marhaba) aey Muhammad ! aey Allah ke rasool ! (marhaba)."
